Lambda Limits
     RAM: 128 MB to 3GB Max
     CPU:
          Is linked to RAM
     Timeout: up to 15min
     /tmp storage: 512 MB (can't process BIG files)
     Deployment package limit: 250MB
Lambda Latency:
     X-Ray can help visualize the end-to-end latency
Lambda Synchronous Invocations: CLI, SDK, API Gateway
Lambda Asynchronous Invocations: S3, SNS, CloudWatch Events, Lambda attempts to retry on errors
Lambda Aliases enable blue/green deployment
CodeDeploy can help you automate traffic shift for Lambda aliases
